animeTitle: Keep a Low Profile, Sect Leader Season 3
otherNames: Keep a Low Profile, Sect Leader, Zhangmen Di Diao Dian,Keep your head down, 掌门低调点
synopsis: Traveling to the world of Tian Xuan, can’t believe I’ve become a useless sect’s leader! Paying money in the city to be reborn in a game’s realm. Making the players my workers, collecting the main characters from the world as my underlings. If we’re talking about being pretentious, then I’ll only take the number one spot!
